Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And I go to Page 10 of Pelvic MRI
And I select 'Finding' radio button

When I select 'Joint effusion in the hip joint' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Right' checkbox is enabled
And 'Left' checkbox is enabled

And 'Little' radio button is enabled
And 'Moderate' radio button is enabled
And 'Strongly pronounced' radio button is enabled

And 'Hemorrhagic' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Hemorrhagic' checkbox
Then 'Sedimentation' checkbox is enabled
